   June 2000

   Mainstreaming ITS Into a Regional Transportation Program (Adobe PDF -
   177 Kb)
   The Maricopa County Department of Transportation ITS Mainstreaming
   Process - presented at ITS America.

   May 2000

   IDAS Brochure (PDF - 2338Kb)
   An introductory brochure from FHWA that explains the ITS Deployment
   Analysis System.

   Be sure to check out the latest additions to our Library - this month
   we have added a series of articles from the December 1999 edition of
   the ITE Journal:
     * Realizing ITS: The Vision vs. The Challenge - ITE Journal, December
       1999 (Adobe PDF - 32 Kb)
     * Transportation Operations--Back to the Future! - ITE Journal,
       December 1999 (Adobe PDF - 20 Kb)
     * Transportation Operations--A Core Mission of the FHWA - ITE
       Journal, December 1999 (Adobe PDF - 34 Kb)
     * The San Francisco Bay Area's Approach to System Management - ITE
       Journal, December 1999 (Adobe PDF - 42 Kb)

   April 2000

   Operations and Management Activities Within the Transportation Planning
   Process (PDF - 28Kb)
   Alan J. DeBlasio and David W. Jackson, ITE Conference, Irvine, CA,
   April 2000
   Since 1997, research staff from the U.S. Department of Transportations
   John A. Volpe National Transportation Systems Center (Volpe Center)
   have been working with the Federal Highway Administrations Office of
   Metropolitan Planning and Programs to assess how operations and
   management activities are incorporated into the metropolitan
   transportation planning process.

   December 1999
     * ITE Journal (December, 1999): Special Issue on Management and
       Operations
     * NCHRP Project 8-36A: Incorporating System Management and Operations
       Practices in Transportation Planning

